description: Creates or updates a DNS zone. Does not modify DNS records within the zone.

subscription_id.description: Specifies the Azure subscription ID, which uniquely identifies the Microsoft Azure subscription.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

zone_name.description: The name of the DNS zone (without a terminating dot).

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to the CreateOrUpdate operation.

if_match.description: The etag of the DNS zone. Omit this value to always overwrite the current zone. Specify the last-seen etag value to prevent accidentally overwriting any concurrent changes.

if_none_match.description: Set to '*' to allow a new DNS zone to be created, but to prevent updating an existing zone. Other values will be ignored.
